application.model

Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.Book

  • public class Book
extends java.lang.Object

    class Book

    This class represents Book objects. It contains BookImage, name, description, hashtags, author, genre, ISBN, format, loaned, dateLoaned, and nameLoaned variables.

    Author:
    bagoferasers

        Book( String BookImage, String name, String description, String hashtags, Author author, String genre, long ISBN, String format, Boolean b, String dateLoaned, String nameLoaned )

        This is a constructor for the Book object and sets variables according to parameters.

        Parameters:
        BookImage - this is the Image path.
        name - this is the name of the book.
        description - this is the book description.
        hashtags - these are the book's hashtags.
        author - this is the book's author.
        genre - this is the book's genre.
        ISBN - this is the book's ISBN.
        format - this is the book's format.
        b - this is the boolean value to see if book is loaned out or not.
        dateLoaned - this is the date the book was loaned.
        nameLoaned - this is the name of person book is loaned to.
